00w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-lockpicking-game-gets-fan-made-free-to-play-spinoff-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-lockpicking-game-gets-fan-made-free-to-play-spinoff-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-lockpicking-game-gets-fan-made-free-to-play-spinoff-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-lockpicking-game-gets-fan-made-free-to-play-spinoff-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-lockpicking-game-gets-fan-made-free-to-play-spinoff-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>感谢粉丝的支持， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/starfield"><em>《Starfield》</em></a>中的开锁小游戏现已成为一款成熟的免费网页游戏。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/boss-level-2023-inon-zur-starfield-score-3500117">伊农·祖尔 (Inon Zur) 如何创造年度最佳视频游戏得分</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.polygon.com/23892696/starfield-digipick-simulator-bb-dev-itch-mobile" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Polygon</em></a>发现，BB-Dev 的<a href="https://bb-dev.itch.io/starfield-digipick-simulator"><em>Starfield Digipick Simulator</em></a>可通过 itch.io 获取，并且也适用于移动设备。事实上，该粉丝最近发布了一个更新，引入了连胜和每日大师级别锁定供玩家尝试完成，类似于<em>Wordle</em>及其衍生品挑战其社区的方式。</p><p> “出于某种原因，Bethesda 游戏总是有很棒的开锁小游戏， <em>Starfield</em>也不例外，” <a href="https://github.com/BBelk/StarfieldDigipickSim">BB-Dev 说</a>。 《Starfield Digipick Simulator》 <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/Starfield/comments/16slije/comment/k2atfaa/?utm_source=share&amp;utm_medium=web2x&amp;context=3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在其他粉丝中引发了一场风暴</a>，其中一位粉丝要求提供该游戏的应用程序版本，以便在旅途中玩。</p><p>然而，BB-Dev 解释说，未经贝塞斯达许可，他们不会开始这方面的工作。 “我希望他们会看到这是开源的，并让它顺其自然。我还想用它做很多事情，我有一个关于无尽模式的想法，这[可能]很酷，” <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/Starfield/comments/16slije/comment/k2atfaa/?utm_source=reddit&amp;utm_medium=web2x&amp;context=3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">他们回答道</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3506588" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3506588" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3506588" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-lockpicking-game-gets-fan-made-free-to-play-spinoff.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-lockpicking-game-gets-fan-made-free-to-play-spinoff.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-lockpicking-game-gets-fan-made-free-to-play-spinoff-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-lockpicking-game-gets-fan-made-free-to-play-spinoff-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-lockpicking-game-gets-fan-made-free-to-play-spinoff-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-lockpicking-game-gets-fan-made-free-to-play-spinoff-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-lockpicking-game-gets-fan-made-free-to-play-spinoff-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3506588" class="wp-caption-text"> “Starfield Digipick Simulator”来源：BB-Dev，来自 Github</figcaption></figure><p>但这并没有阻止他们得出相同的结论。 “未来未来的发展，这将是一款很棒的手机游戏。联系我托德，”BB-Dev 在 Github 上的游戏说明中说道。</p><p> “《 <em>Starfield》</em>让玩家在那个宇宙中实现自己的科幻幻想，” <em>NME</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/starfield-review-3494114">游戏的四星评论</a>中写道。然而，贝塞斯达在推出<em>《Starfield》</em>之前曾对其规模大加赞扬，但最终却成为了其失败的一个因素。</p><p> “有无限多的地方可供参观，但大多数都是相同的——一片无名的研究实验室、矿井和前哨基地的海洋——用几分钟的时间拍摄很有趣，但否则就会被遗忘，”安迪·布朗描述道。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-elder-scrolls-castles-is-a-fallout-shelter-take-on-skyrim-3506492"><em>《上古卷轴：城堡》</em>在 Android 平台上发布了抢先体验版</a>，让玩家有机会管理自己的王国并与“经典的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-elder-scrolls"><em>上古卷轴</em></a>敌人”作战。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www