ttps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-the-1975-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-the-1975-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/matty-healy-the-1975-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matty-healy">马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy)</a>向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975 的</a>歌迷保证，乐队不会解散， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-matty-healy-announces-indefinite-hiatus-from-shows-after-current-tour-ends-3504878">因为他们宣布在全球巡演结束后将“无限期中断”</a> 。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/the-1975-cover-interview-2022-being-funny-in-a-foreign-language-3328010">1975 年：“我宁愿成为假装的超级恶棍，也不愿成为假装的英雄”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 1975 乐队正在进行“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-announce-still-at-their-very-best-2023-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3455360">Still…At Their Very Best</a> ”巡演，以支持他们的最新专辑 2022 年的“Being Fun In A Foreign Language”，该巡演于去年 11 月以“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-debut-dazzling-new-live-show-as-being-funny-in-a-foreign-language-tour-kicks-off-3342776">At Their Very Best</a> ”为标题开始，之后又受到了延期更名。乐队巡演的最后一场演出将于 2024 年 3 月 24 日在阿姆斯特丹举行。</p><p>本周早些时候，这位 1975 年歌手兼吉他手 Healy 宣布乐队将要休息。 “你们都在这里真是太棒了，”他在萨克拉门托金一号中心对人群说道。 “这次巡演结束后，我们将无限期暂停演出，所以今晚有你们和我们在一起真是太棒了。太感谢了。”</p><p>现在，希利澄清说，“无限期中断”就是这个意思。 “我无意暗示我们要分手或类似的事情来吓唬任何铁杆粉丝，”希利在圣何塞 SAP 竞技场对观众说道。</p><p> “这并没有发生。别担心，”他补充道。请参阅下面的片段。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> “我们并不是想吓唬任何铁杆粉丝，我们不会分手” <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/The1975?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#The1975</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/SATVB?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#SATVB</a> <a href="https://t.co/VReejx8Afn">pic.twitter.com/VReejx8Afn</a></p><p> — 1975 TH (@the1975_thteam) <a href="https://twitter.com/the1975_thteam/status/1707624114884936125?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 29 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>上个月，乐队扩展了当前的巡演<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-announce-2024-uk-european-still-at-their-very-best-tour-buy-tickets-3491491">，增加了一系列 2024 年英国和欧洲的演出</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-add-new-dates-to-2024-uk-and-european-still-at-their-very-best-tour-3494798">后来又增加了更多演出</a>。您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-announce-still-at-their-very-best-2023-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3455360">在此处找到完整的日期列表并购买剩余的门票</a>。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/rock/matty-healy-1975-not-splitting-up-hiatus-1235428780/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard</em></a>报道，本周早些时候，当被要求澄清“暂停”是否是巡演计划中的中断，或者对于宣布的暂停是否还有其他解释时，The 1975 的发言人没有发表评论。</p><p>最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-to-stage-worlds-first-carbon-removed-event-at-the-o2-in-london-3494624">证实，乐队将在伦敦 The O2 举办世界首个“去除碳”现场活动</a>。</p><p>本月，The 1975 决定用一段<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-promote-tour-using-fake-matty-healy-political-ad-3502877">由 Healy 主演的模仿美国政治广告的视频</a>来宣传他们的巡演。</p><p>马蒂<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/matty-healy-assures-fans-the-1975-arent-splitting-up-thats-not-happening-3506634">·希利 (Matty Healy) 向粉丝保证 The 1975 不会解散：“那不会发生”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 向女性和有抱负的音乐家分享建议：“你不必表现出色” https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-advice-women-aspiring-musicians-3506540​​?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=billie-eilish-advice-women-aspiring-musiciansKyann-Sian Williams Fri, 29 Sep 2023 13:44:35 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3506540 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “你可以只是一个人，你应该因为只是一个人而获得奖励”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-advice-women-aspiring-musicians-3506540">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 为女性和有抱负的音乐家分享了建议：“你不必表现出色”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/billie-eilish-getty-Nykieria-Chaney_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>向女性同胞和有抱负的艺术家分享了一些建议，告诉她们“不必总是表现出色”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/billie-eilish-cover-interview-2022-glastonbury-festival-3253169">封面上 – Billie Eilish：“我应该为每个人上演一场精彩的格拉斯顿伯里演出”</a></li></ul><p>这位 21 岁的女孩在一次新的采访中回顾了她早期的职业生涯，回忆起她和她的兄弟<a href="/artists/finneas">Finneas</a>在青少年时期“制作这些小歌曲”并试图尽可能与众不同。</p><p>艾利什强调，尽管兄弟姐妹有一个明确的使命，即不“按照任何人说的去做”，但人们不按计划行事也没关系。</p><p> “我必须赞扬我一直以来的样子——我根本不在乎，”她告诉 <a href="https://www.allure.com/story/billie-eilish-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《引诱》</em></a> 。 “我花了很多很多年的时间来说服一屋子的人，让他们相信我会做我知道适合我的事情。我有想法；我有计划。</p><p> “但问题是，人们应该知道——女性也应该知道——你不必表现得特别出色，”她反驳道。 “你可以只是一个人，你应该因为只是一个人而获得奖励。有时艺术家没有计划，这很好，但我有，而且我不会浪费它们。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxvhzMwO_Jx/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div